Customer Service Application
============================

----------
What is it
----------
This is Scooter-powered customer service application. 
See customer service video at http://www.scooterframework.com/screencasts.html for more details.

------------------------------
How to run customerservice app
------------------------------

Run customerservice with default port 8080
linux/mac>%JAVA_HOME%/java -jar tools/server.jar examples/customerservice
windows  >$JAVA_HOME/java  -jar tools/server.jar examples/customerservice

Run customerservice installed in user home directory with port 9090
linux/mac>%JAVA_HOME%/java -jar tools/server.jar /home/joe/customerservice 9090
windows  >$JAVA_HOME/java  -jar tools/server.jar /home/joe/customerservice 9090

Note: "JAVA_HOME" must point to a JDK. This is required by Scooter's autocompiler.
